{"tid":41853,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"高中屁孩家政課打手槍　精液糖霜騙女老師吞下肚","createTime":"2016-12-16T08:16:55.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-17T02:59:30.000Z","uid":48093,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"15c9dce9691c1c73cd87e16ebd359fcaa12726a0","tid":41853,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T08:16:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20161216/640_d49a24060c126ce1890610fa08308eb6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20161216%2F640_d49a24060c126ce1890610fa08308eb6.jpg&h=6b1791ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n國內布拉斯加州奧瑪哈(Omaha)3名高中生，在上家政課時，突發奇想想要惡整老師，趁著空檔跑到廁所打手槍，再用容器盛裝後，混合塗抹在半月型派皮上的糖霜中，接著再請58歲的女老師試吃。<br />\n<br />\n最初未察覺有異狀的女老師將精液糖霜吞下肚後，覺得味道怪怪的，加上事後有偷聽到3名男學生異狀的同學，向她報告有這項陰謀，才發現自己遭到惡整，通知校方。<br />\n<br />\n校方隨即通知警方前往調查，揪出3名惡作劇男學生。據當地警方表示，其中2人坦承自己的惡作劇犯行，而另1人則表示自己在最後一刻打退堂鼓，並沒有成為精液「供應商」之一。對3人犯行，校方發言人彼得森(Brandi Petersen)也表示將全力配合警方調查，但不會透露細節。"},{"pid":"59a6e0e606d311afe714cc2be5509be996c748bf","tid":41853,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T08:18:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c220f67a936cf56b5b9681283401d124e851a60","tid":41853,"uid":17928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T08:22:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n比你條廢老補身仲想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"144514b905f4fe1aca54996bfb3bc292301c931b","tid":41853,"uid":57646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T08:25:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockq